  <heading>RDFFRS</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Return predicate of succesfully loaded elements, setting the condition flags</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction reads the first-fault register (<asm-code>FFR</asm-code>) and places active
elements in the corresponding elements of the destination
predicate. Inactive elements in the destination predicate register are set to zero. This instruction sets the First (N), None (Z), and !Last (C)
condition flags based on the predicate result,
and sets the V flag to zero.</para>
      <para>This instruction is illegal when executed in Streaming SVE mode, unless FEAT_SME_FA64 is implemented and enabled.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>True</predicated>
    <sm_policy>SM_0_only</sm_policy>
  </desc>
